{"content":"---\ntitle: \"<discoveryClientSettings>\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nms.assetid: 02e1b823-a8bb-4074-90d5-8599f71e8f9d\n---\n# \\<discoveryClientSettings>\nContains the settings needed by an application to participate in the service discovery process as a client.  \n  \n\\<system.ServiceModel>  \n\\<standardEndpoints>  \n  \n## Syntax  \n  \n```xml  \n<system.serviceModel>\n  <standardEndpoints>\n    <dynamicEndpoint>\n      <standardEndpoint>\n        <discoveryClientSettings discoveryEndpoint=\"String\">\n          <findCriteria duration=\"TimeSpan\"\n                        maxResults=\"Integer\"\n                        scopeMatchBy=\"Uri\">\n            <contractTypeNames>\n              <add name=\"String\"\n                   namespace=\"String\" />\n            <contractTypeNames>\n            <extensions />\n            <scopes>\n              <add scope=\"URI\"/>\n            </scopes>\n          </findCriteria>\n        </discoveryClientSettings>\n      <standardEndpoint>\n    </dynamicEndpoint>\n  </standardEndpoints>\n</system.serviceModel>\n```  \n  \n## Attributes and Elements  \n The following sections describe attributes, child elements, and parent elements.  \n  \n### Attributes  \n  \n|Attribute|Description|  \n|---------------|-----------------|  \n|discoveryEndpoint|A string that contains the name of the Discovery Endpoint that enables a client application to automatically search for a discoverable service and find its address at runtime.|  \n  \n### Child Elements  \n  \n|Element|Description|  \n|-------------|-----------------|  \n|[\\<standardEndpoints>](../../../../../docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/wcf/standardendpoints.md)|A configuration element that supplies a set of criteria used by a client application to search for a discovery service. Criteria can be grouped into search criteria (specifying what services you’re looking for) and find termination criteria (how long the search should last).|  \n  \n### Parent Elements  \n  \n|Element|Description|  \n|-------------|-----------------|  \n|[\\<standardEndpoints>](../../../../../docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/wcf/standardendpoints.md)|Defines a standard endpoint that contains information to enable an application to function as a client program that can find the endpoint address dynamically at runtime.|  \n  \n## See also\n\n- <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryClientBindingElement>\n- <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.Configuration.DiscoveryClientSettingsElement>\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,109],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"<discoveryClientSettings>\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nms.assetid: 02e1b823-a8bb-4074-90d5-8599f71e8f9d","nodes":[{"content":"<discoveryClientSettings>","nodes":[],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[116,142],"content":"\\<discoveryClientSettings>","linkify":"\\<discoveryClientSettings>","nodes":[{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>discoveryClientSettings&gt;","pos":[0,26],"source":"\\<discoveryClientSettings>"}]},{"content":"Contains the settings needed by an application to participate in the service discovery process as a client.","pos":[143,250]},{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>system.ServiceModel&gt;","pos":[256,278],"source":"\\<system.ServiceModel>"},{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>standardEndpoints&gt;","pos":[281,301],"source":"\\<standardEndpoints>"},{"pos":[310,316],"content":"Syntax","linkify":"Syntax","nodes":[{"content":"Syntax","pos":[0,6]}]},{"pos":[1024,1047],"content":"Attributes and Elements","linkify":"Attributes and Elements","nodes":[{"content":"Attributes and Elements","pos":[0,23]}]},{"content":"The following sections describe attributes, child elements, and parent elements.","pos":[1051,1131]},{"pos":[1141,1151],"content":"Attributes","linkify":"Attributes","nodes":[{"content":"Attributes","pos":[0,10]}]},{"content":"Attribute","pos":[1158,1167]},{"content":"Description","pos":[1168,1179]},{"content":"discoveryEndpo